00:35:48,206 --> 00:35:52,960
I hadn't done my maths homework
or got my test papers signed.

256
00:35:53,086 --> 00:35:55,629
Where did you go?

257
00:35:55,755 --> 00:35:59,175
Nowhere, I just walked around.

258
00:35:59,801 --> 00:36:02,178
