356
00:44:36,984 --> 00:44:40,070
Look at this, his maths test.

357
00:44:40,988 --> 00:44:44,282
Three into nine equals three.
That's all.

358
00:44:44,409 --> 00:44:47,744
Ηe hasn't even attempted
the rest of the test.

359
00:44:49,247 --> 00:44:51,790
Who'd believe
he's Yohan's brother?

360
00:44:59,465 --> 00:45:01,299
- Mr Awasthi...
- Yes?

361
00:45:03,094 --> 00:45:07,681
This is your son's second year
in Grade 3.

362
00:45:07,807 --> 00:45:11,893
At this rate, I won't be able
to help you anymore.

363
00:45:14,897 --> 00:45:17,190
Maybe he has a problem?

364
00:45:18,276 --> 00:45:21,862
