375
00:46:15,541 --> 00:46:20,212
I teach him myself. All day it's,
"Ishaan! Ishaan!"

376
00:46:20,338 --> 00:46:21,630
No, Maya, it's not your fault.

377
00:46:23,925 --> 00:46:26,343
Ηe's not going to learn this way.

378
00:46:28,721 --> 00:46:30,847
OK, I'll be there in the morning.

379
00:46:30,973 --> 00:46:34,893
Thanks a lot Suresh.
Thank you very much. Good night.

380
00:46:37,230 --> 00:46:38,522
Done.

