383
00:46:48,366 --> 00:46:50,492
No, I'm not going to go!

384
00:46:50,618 --> 00:46:55,997
Ishaan, shut up and finish
your dinner quietly! "I won't go."

385
00:46:57,708 --> 00:47:01,378
Let him complete this year
and then...

386
00:47:01,504 --> 00:47:06,258
