388
00:47:11,681 --> 00:47:12,848
Then where will we go?

389
00:47:19,272 --> 00:47:21,606
Look. Look at him glaring.

390
00:47:22,441 --> 00:47:24,442
No regret on his face.

391
00:47:24,569 --> 00:47:26,862
At boarding school
they'll straighten you out!

392
00:47:30,032 --> 00:47:33,952
Today he's got Yohan
to forge a note. What's next?

393
00:47:38,040 --> 00:47:44,004
Trust me. We can't afford the fees,
