409
00:49:02,041 --> 00:49:05,043
I don't want to go
to boarding school.

410
00:49:05,169 --> 00:49:07,879
- You have to.
- I don't want to go!

411
00:49:08,005 --> 00:49:11,549
- Inu, it's not that bad.
- I don't want to go there.

412
00:49:11,676 --> 00:49:15,971
