420
00:50:02,643 --> 00:50:06,021
- You see I'm not scared.
- What are you doing!

421
00:50:06,147 --> 00:50:07,731
I'm not scared!

422
00:50:07,857 --> 00:50:10,442
I will not go!

423
00:50:34,925 --> 00:50:39,095
Your father tells me
you're very stubborn.

424
00:50:39,221 --> 00:50:41,765
Let's get one thing straight.

425
00:50:42,725 --> 00:50:45,143
In this boarding school,
we live by one rule.

426
00:50:45,936 --> 00:50:47,771
Discipline.

427
00:50:48,522 --> 00:50:50,607
Don't worry, Mr Awasthi.

428
00:50:51,776 --> 00:50:54,069
